Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給你拿藥去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛回來就得收拾屋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得好好吃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不吃這些沒用的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我親自調製的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以緩解痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙手像被燒過一樣疼痛難忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到會如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿飛 也就是第三代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他留下的詛咒之傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到她沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是在一個叫短冊街的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短冊街
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們的對手是傳說中的三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂良藥苦口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有什麼竅門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在學校是那種難以集中精力的類型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我現在又有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這張紙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那再看一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是三言兩語能說清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才看白紙的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是看了整張白紙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這次你看的是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是正中央的點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你只是看白紙的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以視線會飄忽不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果上面出現一個點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的意志就會集中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是集中於一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意志一旦集中 精神就會安定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以引發意想不到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才弄破橡膠球的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上應該積蓄了大量的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你努力集中精力的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要集中就會引發力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果沒有任何標記 就會很難集中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是竅門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你要在右手蓄積查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後努力將它集中在這個標記上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉標誌與護額
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過破了個洞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你打聽個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼集中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的猿飛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去收集情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間是不能浪費的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為師父 都不跟徒弟心靈交流一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 接著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 交流完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管好色仙人了 我自己練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你必須自己完成這次的修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該努力向第四代靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己把握吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在會在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不必
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大姐讓我賺了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是傳說中的肥羊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可能還在賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短冊街 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的雙手終於有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管是良藥 可也少不了吃一番苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7 7 7…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7 7 7…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜客官 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,44號台的女士中了三七連線大獎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜44號台的女士中大獎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊 綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然中了三個7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自歎不如啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了 又中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然會中頭彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於綱手大人 我還是瞭解一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也是醫療班的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說她第一個提出常規的四人小組中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:12:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須增加一名醫療專家的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的方案非常完善
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不具備恢復能力的純戰鬥小組
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上戰場會有怎樣的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不言而喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上獲得的戰鬥經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催生了這個提案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有大量的犧牲 所以才想到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們總是在失去很多東西之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才瞭解到事情的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能被人稱為醫療專家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及傳說中的三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為…這種犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須再集中點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼集中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 好球…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼可笑的表情 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不停地浮現在腦海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我怎麼集中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有哪個姑娘在嘀咕我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 綱手大人收穫滿滿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是奇跡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還悶悶不樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鎮子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不祥之兆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是觀光勝地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好好轉轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊看完走人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快把事情搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過分點也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼得無法集中查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一會兒 就休息一小會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課還沒上完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們總是不集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼能成為出色的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能一直坐在那兒不動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 要訓的話 請長話短說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後要專門為你們\N開設一門訓練集中力的課
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在需要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是木葉的前輩們\N每天都在做的集中力訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把注意力集中到額前的樹葉上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後製造查克拉的修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將精力集中到樹葉上的一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓自己不會分散注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是自古流傳下來的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有能夠集中精神的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能成為出色的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是護額上木葉標誌的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼聽都不像真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓我們拿出動力才胡謅的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是胡謅的 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要集中就能成為出色的忍者咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂出色的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指非常厲害的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會做這種傻事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點聽伊魯卡老師的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其反省不如行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中 集中 集中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短冊城還真是壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是文化遺產啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說的那麼悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人也應該好好看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正看看也不用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股寒意是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉的密度居然高到灼傷了自己的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真嚇了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二階段結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快進行第三階段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們要去找綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼第三階段可以一邊走一邊練的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不快點又找不到綱手了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時可就後悔莫及了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去制高點找 只要在鎮上都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬到城堡上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.09,0:22:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就在那邊嗎 你沒看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 波紋
